readme:
Service Usage

This service is used to retrieve various details from the application form lodged to obtain an Australian Business Travel Card. Various information that can be returned includes License information (Firearms and/or Drivers), Bio details and Address information.

Service Behaviour

This service will retrieve information from the form created in SV113. This service will interact with ABTC using the Transaction Reference Number supplied in SV113. This is a synchronis service.
